{"id":294355,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/05/维权网-长沙同性恋游行组织者被拘留、律师指处/","date":"2013-05-20T11:31:35Z","modified":"2013-05-20T11:31:35Z","title":"维权网 | 长沙同性恋游行组织者被拘留、律师指处罚多处违法（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"></p>\n<div><span></span></div>\n<p><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a><span lang=\"EN-US\"><span>（维权网信息员李军报道）</span>2013</span><span>年</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">17</span><span>日</span><span>是“国际不再恐同日”，</span><span> </span><span>有近百位来自全国的同性恋支持者在长沙举行“同志”反歧视街头游行活动。当天下午两点，这支队伍拿着彩旗，喊着口号从长沙潇湘大道沿江风光带走过。活动发起人向愈韩曾表示，活动的意义主要是希望向社会传达同性恋群体积极向上的生活现状。</span></p>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日</span><span>，长沙市公安局岳麓分局对向愈韩作出行政拘留</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span><span>日的处罚。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">19</span><span>日</span><span>，向愈韩的两位朋友找到蔺其磊律师，把签好的律师委托书送来，委托其为向愈韩代理。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span lang=\"EN-US\">5</span><span>月</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">20</span><span>日</span><span>上午，蔺其磊律师和贺刚律师在长沙市拘留所会见了被拘留的向愈韩，他说</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">18</span><span>日以来至今没有吃饭，没人给他充值卡，他是他母亲的监护人，他母亲一人现在长沙无人管护，语言沟通难，但要求打电话告诉朋友去照顾母亲，未被允许。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><span>蔺其磊律师表示对向愈韩的处罚多处违法，在民主国家游行示威是公民天然权利，律师要帮助当事人理顺权利，彰显宪法，宪法上公民游行示威的权利何时才能从纸上变为真实的权利。</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-d0Lrn-Aa06Y/UZnUwWERKiI/AAAAAAAAiRI/mtAIlMkyXeU/s1600/1.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"221\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-d0Lrn-Aa06Y/UZnUwWERKiI/AAAAAAAAiRI/mtAIlMkyXeU/s400/1.jpg\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>\n<p></p>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-edpQRGm9MCQ/UZnUyZGXsyI/AAAAAAAAiRQ/PWc07R4m2uE/s1600/2.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"217\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-edpQRGm9MCQ/UZnUyZGXsyI/AAAAAAAAiRQ/PWc07R4m2uE/s400/2.jpg\" width=\"400\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=2ea93c5b7b\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/msuvD\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[19196]}